Today, Satpol PP blockades the zebra cross in the Sudirman area, where the Citayam Fashion Week usually takes place. In a video taken by at/ @aan.chid on Tiktok, it was seen that Satpol PP ordered citizens to clear the area because a zebra cross is used to cross the street and not for fashion show. Barriers were put near the zebra cross, and police officers were put on standby in Sudirman.

node.text: Actress Nana Mirdad saved a newborn baby in the bushes near her house. According to Nana via her Instagram Stroy, one of her house maid found the baby and told Nana about it, she then immediately brought the baby to the hospital to be taken care of. The baby appeared to be just born the morning before she was found in the bushes with its umbilical cord still intact. Thank you for taking care and giving love to this newborn baby, @nanamirdad_ 🤍🤍🤍😭😭😭

node.text: The infamous Karen's Diner that went viral for their unique service has closed after for operating less than a year. Early last year, Karen's Diner opened with an out of the box concept where customers are greeted by rude staffs and given unpleasant dining experience. Bedwina Baptista, an employee of Karen's Diner explained that this is due to its expiring contract which only lasted for 6 months. What do you think? 🤔🤔

node.text: Who says two different personalities can't be compatible? In fact, exciting stories will emerge between them. Say @vidialdiano and @sheiladaisha, two people with opposite personalities with their own tastes, including home decoration. But they can find harmony at @informaid, which provides various kinds of home furniture for all people's tastes. Can you imagine ​​what it would be like to live with someone with a different personality than you? It will be fun! #PastiKetemu 👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻🫶🫶🤍🤍
